This is a fork of an IRC-bot used by werebuild: http://werebuild.eu/wiki/John-Henry

The code needed some updates. 

[CHANGELOG]

- updated to ttytter for oauth support
- added !tell for message relaying
- added custom !postevent to the hspbp.org tiki calendar
- added whitelisting support
- some small fixes
- added dreams and some personality
- added an award system
